cs.MOBILE, cs.SY, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG

Reasoning: 
- cs.MOBILE is the most likely category as the paper focuses on a localization system for smartphones.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of sensors and prediction models to improve localization accuracy.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of landmarks detected automatically to improve localization accuracy.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of special driving patterns from inertial sensory data to improve localization accuracy.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of linear regression to build a prediction model.
